sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as System Admin
    participant UI as User Admin UI
    participant API as User/RBAC API
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as User DB
    participant Policy as Permission Engine
    participant Log as Audit Log

    Admin->>UI: Gan role/permission cho user
    UI->>API: PUT /users/{id}/roles
    API->>Auth: Xac thuc admin va lay claims
    API->>Policy: Kiem tra quyen manage_users
    alt Du quyen
        API->>DB: Cap nhat roles, permissions
        API->>Auth: Invalidate/refresh token neu can
        API->>Log: Ghi audit RBAC
        API-->>UI: Cap nhat thanh cong
    else Khong du quyen
        API-->>UI: 403 Forbidden
    end
